The '''temple city''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the planet [[Aridka]]. The city was surrounded by cliffs, upon which stood the ruins of [[temple]]s and [[obelisk]]s.

Around [[22 BBY/Legends|21.5 BBY]], nine [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] made their [[Battle of Aridka|last stand]] against the [[Separatist Droid Army/Legends|Separatist Droid Army]] on the outskirts of the city. The clones erected a [[Deflector shield/Legends|deflector shield]] at their final position to defend a bridge leading directly into the city. Upon the arrival of [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Plo Koon/Legends|Plo Koon]], the troops managed to defeat the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]] and save the city.

